description: The uwucomet Insignia is a thank you reward to those who commissioned from our community artists during our [Recomet collaboration](https://twitter.com/uwucrewnft/status/1661509646543208448)!. This Insignia grants you access to 4 special dressing room items: Celestial Dress (Outfit), Celestial Hairpiece (Hat), Celestial Staff (Right Accessory), and Celestial Sky (Background)!
